snippet.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
snippet.description:
New game drops! Developers! More!

Minecraft LIVE is our own super special show that gives you the inside info on everything happening in the world of Minecraft! 

We‚Äôre updating vanilla Minecraft with multiple game drops per year, so we now host two of these shows to cover all the new features. Every episode includes fresh info from our developers, the inside scoop on unannounced upcoming game drops, and more! 

After the broadcast, stay tuned in for the Deep Dig After Show where our developers and guests show off the new features, often resulting in chaos. Vu Bui will return as host and attempt to keep things running smoothly. Good luck to that guy!

American Sign Language: https://www.youtube.com/live/W3uQA_unm0I
British Sign Language: https://youtube.com/live/ZygMYm2sx5U
Audio Descriptions: https://youtube.com/live/DoXrLv__PAY

Check out Minecraft.net for more information!  
https://www.minecraft.net/

How I "DIED" on a Hardcore Minecraft SMP

inspired by @4CVIT's naked and afraid series!

thank you to:  @Boosfer @loppezz @FlameFragsMC eggchan @LettuceK @Twirps as well as all of the capital city guards and merchant city players!

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of my music is by AZALI so check him out!)
https://www.youtube.com/@nombra101 (song during the first flame fight!)

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

thank you to:  @Boosfer @loppezz @FlameFragsMC eggchan @LettuceK @Twirps as well as all of the capital city guards and merchant city players!

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of my music is by AZALI so check him out!)

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

snippet.title: BELLES VILLAIN SONG (Pt 2) - Reclaim My Story | Official Animatic Video | by Lydia the Bard & Frost
snippet.description:
BELLES VILLAIN SONG (Part 2) - Reclaim my Story | Official Animatic Music Video | By Lydia the Bard and Frostudio Chambersonic

STREAM SONG HERE - https://ffm.to/bellepart2
PRESAVE MY DEBUT ALBUM - https://ffm.to/thewoodsdebutalbum.OYD
WATCH PART 1 - https://youtu.be/xFByIo6nujM?si=oM01ONNnR-3IXosb

It‚Äôs the last Villain song for a little while now! (Don‚Äôt worry they‚Äôll be back) I hope you enjoy this extension to Belles story! It felt like Gaston for sure needed dealing with after the last one! Following this release the next thing I‚Äôll be posting is my album AAAHH

If you dont already know I‚Äôm releasing my debut album ‚ÄòThe Woods‚Äô on October 11th!! SO EXCITED I CANT EVEN BEGIN TO SAY HOW EXCITED I AM FOR YOU TO HEAR IT AAAHAHAHAH. You can presave here - https://ffm.to/thewoodsdebutalbum.OYDhttps:/ Also I hope you enjoyed the conclusion to Figs restaurant dream story aswell!! I think I‚Äôll open him a restaurant either way. Now enough waffle, the story!

BELLES VILLAIN STORY 

Belle was always the odd one out, the outcast, the outsider. Her whole life she put up with those in her village making fun of her and her Father, so she stayed hidden behind her books. Biding her time. Waiting for the right moment.

That time finally arrived when she was kidnapped by the beast, just another man trying to control her, to tame her. She‚Äôd put up with that from Gaston for years and so another man mistreating her was nothing new. The beast found that out very quickly. Belle didn‚Äôt allow herself to fall in love with him, only let the beast think that. And when her time finally claim she plucked every last petal off that rose and watched as he became a Beast forever. You might question, why, if the beast was now a monster, did he not then attack Belle? Well, that would‚Äôve happened, but Belle wasn‚Äôt just anyone, Belle had the blood of the women who cast that curse running through her veins. Belle was the enchantresses daughter. 

Now with a Beast ready to attack anyone she willed Belle sets her sights on the town, on Gaston, on her father. Those who run her mother out of the village, the man who tried to force himself upon her, and her father, who was too distracted making his inventions to intervene. Belle has always known she was superior to them, well now it was time to show them just how superior she was. She‚Äôll have her revenge, and then she‚Äôll take her rightful place, as their new God. 

LYRICS

Gosh it disturbs me to see you Gaston
My you look so gaunt
Much has changed since our last meeting Gaston
I‚Äôm no longer a debutante
That monster you were so scared about
He‚Äôs my ally now
Only monster left that I can see around
Stands in front of this crowd

You mocked and harassed
And made pass after pass
And when that didn‚Äôt work you planned forceful attacks
So let‚Äôs end this fantasy 
Write a new tragedy
And sweetheart
You don‚Äôt last the first act

Ill reclaim my story
Take back the end you‚Äôve been hoarding
Delicate words are boring
Tear those pages out-law vain glory
Strike through the cruel and the haughty
I have the pen and authority
Im the author now

But I‚Äôd be remiss to pin this all on you
How could I forget
All these friendly faces, step out, join us too
Come up and meet my new pet
Hold out your hand I swear he won‚Äôt bite
Unless I say so
Come to think it didn‚Äôt you all stand aside
When we needed you most

I‚Äôll remake my past
Change the lines I‚Äôll recast
As the actors are fired and beats are rehashed
Im done with collaborative
I run the narrative
And my word is fact

Ill reclaim my story
Take back the end you‚Äôve been hoarding
Delicate words are boring
Tear those pages out-law vain glory
Strike through the cruel and the haughty
I have the pen and authority
Im the author now

Patient as I watched you drag behind
Throwing hate cos I had the sharper mind
Jealous words are easy to undermine
Wanna be me? Maybe read a book sometime
While you go write your name in the sand
Im charting stars and Im writing psalms
Even Gods above seem to understand
I‚Äôll hold this whole world in my hand
So save yourself and accept defeat
Your tale is done now go take a seat
And watch and maybe you‚Äôll learn something
Don‚Äôt judge a songbird till she sings
You want me squashed just to save your pride
But I gotta thank you for all the lies
Cos now I finally realise

I am the God your Gods left behind

Ill claim my story
Take back my story
Ill do as you taught me
I‚Äôll claim my story
Now!


‚ú®CREDITS‚ú®

Vocals / Lyrics - Lydia the Bard 

Music - ‚Äã‚Å†@FrostudioChambersonic 

Animatic - ‚Ä™Luck Buggy - https://www.instagram.com/luck.buggy?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw==

Ending ad
Instrumental - Ben Tomalin 
Animatic - Zobeebop - https://www.instagram.com/zobeebop?igsh=MWVxZ3RsaDN2enBjaA==
Fig voice - Alex Runicles

snippet.title: Wicked: For Good | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
The final #WickedForGood trailer is here ‚ú® Watch now.

Pre-order Wicked: For Good - The Soundtrack üíöü©∑ available November 21st at https://wickedthesoundtrack.lnk.to/forgood
-----
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@wickedmovie
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/wickedmovie
X: https://twitter.com/wickedmovie
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wickedmovie
Official Site: https://wickedmovie.com

And now whatever way our stories end, I know you have rewritten mine by being my friend ‚Ä¶

Last year‚Äôs global cinematic cultural sensation, which became the most successful Broadway film adaptation of all time, now reaches its epic, electrifying, emotional conclusion in Wicked: For Good. 

Directed once again by award-winning director Jon M. Chu and starring the spectacular returning cast, led by Academy Award¬Æ nominated superstars Cynthia Erivo and Ariana Grande, the final chapter of the untold story of the witches of Oz begins with Elphaba and Glinda estranged and living with the consequences of their choices. 

Elphaba (Cynthia Erivo), now demonized as The Wicked Witch of the West, lives in exile, hidden within the Ozian forest while continuing her fight for the freedom of Oz‚Äôs silenced Animals and desperately trying to expose the truth she knows about The Wizard (Jeff Goldblum).  

Glinda, meanwhile, has become the glamorous symbol of Goodness for all of Oz, living at the palace in Emerald City and reveling in the perks of fame and popularity. Under the instruction of Madame Morrible (Oscar¬Æ winner Michelle Yeoh), Glinda is deployed to serve as an effervescent comfort to Oz, reassuring the masses that all is well under the rule of The Wizard.  

As Glinda‚Äôs stardom expands and she prepares to marry Prince Fiyero (Olivier award winner and Emmy and SAG nominee Jonathan Bailey) in a spectacular Ozian wedding, she is haunted by her separation from Elphaba. She attempts to broker a conciliation between Elphaba and The Wizard, but those efforts will fail, driving Elphaba and Glinda only further apart. The aftershocks will transform Boq (Tony nominee Ethan Slater) and Fiyero forever, and threaten the safety of Elphaba‚Äôs sister, Nessarose (Marissa Bode), when a girl from Kansas comes crashing into all their lives. 

As an angry mob rises against the Wicked Witch, Glinda and Elphaba will need to come together one final time. With their singular friendship now the fulcrum of their futures, they will need to truly see each other, with honesty and empathy, if they are to change themselves, and all of Oz, for good. 

Wicked: For Good also stars Emmy nominee Bowen Yang and Bronwyn James as Glinda‚Äôs fawning assistants, Pfannee and ShenShen and BAFTA and Grammy nominee Sharon D. Clarke (Caroline, or Change) as the voice of Elphaba‚Äôs childhood nanny, Dulcibear. 

The film is produced by returning Tony and Emmy winning powerhouse Marc Platt p.g.a. and by multiple Tony winner David Stone. The executive producers are Stephen Schwartz, David Nicksay, Jared LeBoff, Winnie Holzman and Dana Fox. The first film, Wicked, released in November 2024, earned 10 Academy Award¬Æ nominations, including Best Picture, and won the Oscars¬Æ for Costume Design and Production Design. To date, the film has grossed $750 million worldwide. 

Wicked: For Good is based on the generation-defining musical stage play with music and lyrics by legendary Grammy and Oscar¬Æ winning composer and lyricist Stephen Schwartz and book by Winnie Holzman, from the bestselling novel by Gregory Maguire. The screenplay is by Winnie Holzman and Winnie Holzman & Dana Fox. The film score is by John Powell & Stephen Schwartz, with music and lyrics by Stephen Schwartz.

Enchantress, Joker, Ben Affleck Batman Changes, Harley Quinn, Ending Explained, Post Credit Scene. Superman Flashbacks, Batman and Gotham City References explained. Justice Gang, Superman, Justice League Changes to season 1 with The Flash & Aquaman Scene, Green Lantern, Hawkgirl, Maxwell Lord. Multiverse Crossover DCEU to DCU reboot jokes and references. Peacemaker Season 2 Episode 5 Trailer. 

Superman Easter Eggs. James Gunn new Justice League explained. Fortress Of Solitude, Bradley Cooper Jor-El Cameo Scene, Kelex Robots, New Scenes. New Batman Changes and DC Movies Plan for Batman Explained. New Footage and Scenes. Fortress of Solitude. Superman vs Ultraman, Evil Superman. Green Lantern First Look. Mr Terrific Krypto Scene. Superman vs Lex Luthor, New Footage, Superman Legacy 2025 Teaser. New Superman Suit, The Flash Returns Explained. Milly Alcock Supergirl. New Supergirl vs Previous versions. Supergirl Woman of Tomorrow Movie Teaser. David Corenswet Superman, Nicholas Hoult Lex Luthor Explained, changes from previous versions of Lex Luthor like Man of Steel, Batman v Superman, Justice League. The Authority. Superman Legacy Plot and Story Explained. New Supergirl Explained.

Batman Brave and the Bold Teaser and the New Batman will be announced next year. Batman Brave and the Bold Teaser and the New Batman will be announced next year. Nathan Fillion Green Lantern, Hawkgirl, Mr Terrific and more new Justice League characters. Why The New Justice League is based more on the Animated Justice League Team.

Jason Momoa Lobo Explained. Henry Cavill Superman Future Plans, Deleted Scenes. Batman Brave and the Bold James Gunn DCEU Reboot Explained. Lots more DC and Marvel Trailers coming Superman Trailer 2025, Avengers 5 Doomsday Trailer, Spider-Man Brand New Day Trailer & Superman Supergirl Trailer soon too!

–ü–∞—Å—Ö–∞–ª–∫–∏ –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω–∞. –ü–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –Ω–æ–≤–æ—ó –õ—ñ–≥–∏ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç—ñ –∑ –î–∂–µ–π–º—Å–æ–º –ì–∞–Ω–Ω–æ–º. –§–æ—Ä—Ç–µ—Ü—è –°–∞–º–æ—Ç–Ω–æ—Å—Ç—ñ, –∫–∞–º–µ–æ –ë—Ä–µ–¥–ª—ñ –ö—É–ø–µ—Ä–∞ –∑ –î–∂–æ—Ä-–ï–ª–æ–º, —Ä–æ–±–æ—Ç–∏ Kelex, –Ω–æ–≤—ñ —Å—Ü–µ–Ω–∏. –ù–æ–≤—ñ –∑–º—ñ–Ω–∏ –ë–µ—Ç–º–µ–Ω–∞ —Ç–∞ –ø–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –ø–ª–∞–Ω—É —Ñ—ñ–ª—å–º—ñ–≤ DC —â–æ–¥–æ –ë–µ—Ç–º–µ–Ω–∞. –ù–æ–≤—ñ –∫–∞–¥—Ä–∏ —Ç–∞ —Å—Ü–µ–Ω–∏. –§–æ—Ä—Ç–µ—Ü—è –°–∞–º–æ—Ç–Ω–æ—Å—Ç—ñ. –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω –ø—Ä–æ—Ç–∏ –£–ª—å—Ç—Ä–∞–º–µ–Ω–∞, –ó–ª–∏–π –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω. –ü–µ—Ä—à–∏–π –ø–æ–≥–ª—è–¥ –Ω–∞ –ó–µ–ª–µ–Ω–æ–≥–æ –õ—ñ—Ö—Ç–∞—Ä—è. –°—Ü–µ–Ω–∞ –∑ –ú—ñ—Å—Ç–µ—Ä–æ–º –ß—É–¥–æ–≤–∏–º –ö—Ä–∏–ø—Ç–æ. –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω –ø—Ä–æ—Ç–∏ –õ–µ–∫—Å–∞ –õ—é—Ç–æ—Ä–∞, –Ω–æ–≤—ñ –∫–∞–¥—Ä–∏, —Ç–∏–∑–µ—Ä —Ñ—ñ–ª—å–º—É ¬´–°–ø–∞–¥—â–∏–Ω–∞ –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω–∞ 2025¬ª. –ù–æ–≤–∏–π –∫–æ—Å—Ç—é–º –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω–∞, –ø–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è ¬´–ü–æ–≤–µ—Ä–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –§–ª–µ—à–∞¬ª. –ú—ñ–ª–ª—ñ –ê–ª–∫–æ–∫: –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–¥—ñ–≤—á–∏–Ω–∞. –ù–æ–≤–∞ –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–¥—ñ–≤—á–∏–Ω–∞ –ø—Ä–æ—Ç–∏ –ø–æ–ø–µ—Ä–µ–¥–Ω—ñ—Ö –≤–µ—Ä—Å—ñ–π. –¢–∏–∑–µ—Ä —Ñ—ñ–ª—å–º—É ¬´–°—É–ø–µ—Ä–¥—ñ–≤—á–∏–Ω–∞: –ñ—ñ–Ω–∫–∞ –∑–∞–≤—Ç—Ä–∞—à–Ω—å–æ–≥–æ –¥–Ω—è¬ª. –î–µ–≤—ñ–¥ –ö–æ—Ä–µ–Ω—Å–≤–µ—Ç: –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω, –ù—ñ–∫–æ–ª–∞—Å –ì–æ–ª—Ç: –ø–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –õ–µ–∫—Å–∞ –õ—é—Ç–æ—Ä–∞, –∑–º—ñ–Ω–∏ –ø–æ—Ä—ñ–≤–Ω—è–Ω–æ –∑ –ø–æ–ø–µ—Ä–µ–¥–Ω—ñ–º–∏ –≤–µ—Ä—Å—ñ—è–º–∏ –õ–µ–∫—Å–∞ –õ—é—Ç–æ—Ä–∞, —Ç–∞–∫—ñ —è–∫ ¬´–õ—é–¥–∏–Ω–∞ –∑—ñ —Å—Ç–∞–ª—ñ¬ª, ¬´–ë–µ—Ç–º–µ–Ω –ø—Ä–æ—Ç–∏ –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω–∞¬ª, ¬´–õ—ñ–≥–∞ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç—ñ¬ª. –ê–≤—Ç–æ—Ä–∏—Ç–µ—Ç. –ü–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è —Å—é–∂–µ—Ç—É —Ç–∞ —ñ—Å—Ç–æ—Ä—ñ—ó ¬´–°–ø–∞–¥—â–∏–Ω–∏ –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω–∞¬ª. –ü–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –Ω–æ–≤–æ—ó –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–¥—ñ–≤—á–∏–Ω–∏.

–¢–∏–∑–µ—Ä —Ñ—ñ–ª—å–º—É ¬´–•–æ—Ä–æ–±—Ä–∏–π —ñ —Å–º—ñ–ª–∏–≤–∏–π –ë–µ—Ç–º–µ–Ω¬ª —Ç–∞ ¬´–ù–æ–≤–∏–π –ë–µ—Ç–º–µ–Ω¬ª –±—É–¥—É—Ç—å –∞–Ω–æ–Ω—Å–æ–≤–∞–Ω—ñ –Ω–∞—Å—Ç—É–ø–Ω–æ–≥–æ —Ä–æ–∫—É. –¢–∏–∑–µ—Ä ¬´–ë–µ—Ç–º–µ–Ω: –•–æ—Ä–æ–±—Ä–∏–π —Ç–∞ —Å–º—ñ–ª–∏–≤–∏–π¬ª —ñ ¬´–ù–æ–≤–∏–π –ë–µ—Ç–º–µ–Ω¬ª –±—É–¥—É—Ç—å –∞–Ω–æ–Ω—Å–æ–≤–∞–Ω—ñ –Ω–∞—Å—Ç—É–ø–Ω–æ–≥–æ —Ä–æ–∫—É. –ù–∞—Ç–∞–Ω –§—ñ–ª–ª—ñ–æ–Ω, –ó–µ–ª–µ–Ω–∏–π –õ—ñ—Ö—Ç–∞—Ä, –Ø—Å—Ç—Ä—É–±-–î—ñ–≤—á–∏–Ω–∞, –ú—ñ—Å—Ç–µ—Ä –¢–µ—Ä—Ä—ñ—Ñ—ñ–∫ —Ç–∞ —ñ–Ω—à—ñ –Ω–æ–≤—ñ –ø–µ—Ä—Å–æ–Ω–∞–∂—ñ –õ—ñ–≥–∏ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç—ñ. –ß–æ–º—É ¬´–ù–æ–≤–∞ –õ—ñ–≥–∞ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç—ñ¬ª –±—ñ–ª—å—à–µ –±–∞–∑—É—î—Ç—å—Å—è –Ω–∞ –∞–Ω—ñ–º–æ–≤–∞–Ω—ñ–π –∫–æ–º–∞–Ω–¥—ñ –õ—ñ–≥–∏ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç—ñ.

–ü–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –î–∂–µ–π—Å–æ–Ω–∞ –ú–æ–º–æ–∞ —Ç–∞ –õ–æ–±–æ. –ì–µ–Ω—Ä—ñ –ö–∞–≤—ñ–ª–ª, –ø–ª–∞–Ω–∏ –Ω–∞ –º–∞–π–±—É—Ç–Ω—î –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω–∞, –≤–∏–¥–∞–ª–µ–Ω—ñ —Å—Ü–µ–Ω–∏. –ü–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –ø–µ—Ä–µ–∑–∞–ø—É—Å–∫—É DCEU –î–∂–µ–π–º—Å–∞ –ì–∞–Ω–Ω–∞. –©–µ –±–∞–≥–∞—Ç–æ —Ç—Ä–µ–π–ª–µ—Ä—ñ–≤ DC —Ç–∞ Marvel: —Ç—Ä–µ–π–ª–µ—Ä –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω–∞ 2025 —Ä–æ–∫—É, —Ç—Ä–µ–π–ª–µ—Ä ¬´–ú–µ—Å–Ω–∏–∫—ñ–≤ 5: –°—É–¥–Ω–∏–π –¥–µ–Ω—å¬ª, —Ç—Ä–µ–π–ª–µ—Ä ¬´–õ—é–¥–∏–Ω–∏-–ø–∞–≤—É–∫–∞: –ù–æ–≤–∏–π –¥–µ–Ω—å¬ª —Ç–∞ —Ç—Ä–µ–π–ª–µ—Ä –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω–∞: –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–≥–µ—Ä–ª!

snippet.description:
Find out more about the Update in the articles below!
üì∞ https://supr.cl/Update_Oct25

X ‚ñ∫ https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/

TikTok ‚ñ∫ https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale
Facebook ‚ñ∫ https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale

P1Harmony is set to release their English Album 'EX' on September 26.

'EX' is based on the concept of a quirky ‚ÄúGame Lovers Club," portraying the members‚Äô experiences of ‚Äúlove‚Äù through the lens of digital games. With this album, P1Harmony presents a fresh and playful visual identity‚Äîcute and lovable yet uniquely conceptual and full of character.

The title track ‚ÄúEX‚Äù is a synth-pop song characterized by its addictive melody, refreshing synth
sounds, and the dynamic vocals of P1Harmony members. The lyrics express the realization that the emotions once shared were truly special‚Äîunlike fleeting relationships of the past‚Äîand convey a heartfelt plea to stop wandering and embrace an earnest confession of love. With its easy listening appeal, "EX" blends a soft melody with intricate digital sound design, creating a smooth yet distinctive listening experience.

The choreography of ‚ÄúEX‚Äù also carries layered meaning, reflecting the witty way the lyrics reinterpret sadness. The word ‚ÄúEX‚Äù is expressed through X-shaped movements, while one hand points to ‚Äúme‚Äù and the other to ‚Äúyou,‚Äù symbolizing distance and difference between two people. Renowned for their powerful performances, P1Harmony interprets the choreography with finesse, creating perfect synergy with the song. Fans may also enjoy spotting how many times the X-shape move appears throughout the performance.

The music video depicts P1Harmony overcoming heartbreak with a playful spirit. As members of the Game Lovers Club, the group receives an unexpected breakup message while hanging out in their hideout. Instead of falling into sorrow, they approach the situation in their own unique ways, even transforming the pain of separation into a game, radiating bright and uplifting energy. With this concept, P1Harmony showcases a refreshing contrast to their usual powerful image.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: ULTRAKILL 94 - Deathcatcher
snippet.description:
Deathcatchers are a rare enemy that causes all nearby dead foes to get resurrected until it's destroyed.
The resurrected versions are slightly slower and weaker, but as the dead stack up, their numbers can easily become overwhelming.

snippet.title: TH vs. GX ‚Äî VALORANT Champions Paris ‚Äî Playoffs Stage
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world‚Äôs top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We‚Äôre proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:
Twitter/X: @valorantesports
Facebook: /valorantesports
Instagram: @valorantesports
TikTok: @valorantesports
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/valorant
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@ValorantEsports
Photos from the Event: https://www.flickr.com/photos/valorantesports/
Official VALORANT Esports News: https://valorantesports.com/news
Web: https://valorantesports.com

snippet.title: 8 Pro Speedrunners vs 1 Secret Cheater
snippet.description:
I've gathered 9 pro speedrunners to race against eachother, but one is secretly cheating in creative mode. Can the pros figure out who is cheating, or will the imposter be able to Craft A Lie?

CREDITS:
Editing: @biggestbee 

Players:
Aquacorde: @Aquacorde https://twitch.tv/aquacordeMC
Automatt: @AutomattPL https://twitch.tv/AutomattPL
Mongey: @bigbigmongey https://www.twitch.tv/bigbigmongey
Doogile: @Doogile https://www.twitch.tv/doogile
Erik: @Erikfzf https://www.twitch.tv/erikfzf
Feinberg: @FeinbergMC https://www.twitch.tv/feinberg
Hax: @hackingnoises https://www.twitch.tv/hackingnoisess
Infume: @infumemc https://www.twitch.tv/infume
Silverr: @silverrruns https://www.twitch.tv/silverrruns

My Twitch: 
https://twitch.tv/nerdi

POST MATCH DISCUSSION:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mJOqZ0N6hew

Music from Silksong/Hollow Knight OSTs & Epidemic Sound

RULES:
9 players will all be in a private Ranked lobby. Each round, the slowest player to complete the seed is eliminated*. Secretly, one of the 9 is going to be in creative mode (the imposter) for every round. They will have an additional side task each new round (e.g. place 64 diamond blocks) that they must complete before entering the end fountain. After a seed is played, the remaining players will discuss the seed for 3 minutes and choose to either vote out a player or pass. The player with the most votes will be eliminated; if it is a tie, then no players will be eliminated. If the runners vote out the imposter, they win. If the imposter survives until there is only 1 other runner left, then they win. 

*There will also be a time limit (15min), so if several runners do not finish the seed, the runner further behind in the splits will be eliminated. If there are several runners stuck in the same split, one will randomly be eliminated; this rule will also be applied to the creative mode runner if they do not finish the seed.

Some additional things:
-Advancements will be on for all players. So the imposter must be careful about doing things too quickly or obtaining random advancements.

-The creative mode runner is not allowed to use commands or the extra saved hotbars.

-The creative mode runner may choose not to complete the seed, but get far enough into it that they are not eliminated if they notice several runners dying. So, if you see a player not finish a seed, they could still be the imposter.

This is Minecraft, but Steve is learning the Sad Story of the DEER! When Steve discovers the Deer‚Äôs story tied to a scientists and all the other children, showing the past of the Deer kid. He needs to discover their secrets and mysteries! This is The Sad Story of the DEER in Minecraft...

MORE CHECKPOINT ADVENTURES:

‚Ä£ MINECRAFT DIMENSION: https://bit.ly/3mKfUOL


¬¨

Minecraft is an open world game that has no specific goals for the player to accomplish, allowing players a large amount of freedom in choosing how to play the game however, there is an achievement system. The gameplay by default is first person, but players have the option to play in third person mode. The core gameplay revolves around breaking and placing blocks. The game world is essentially composed of rough 3D objects‚Äîmainly cubes‚Äîthat are arranged in a fixed grid pattern and represent different materials, such as dirt, stone, various ores, water, and tree trunks. While players can move freely across the world, objects and items can only be placed at fixed locations relative to the grid. Players can gather these material blocks and place them elsewhere, thus allowing for various constructions.

The gameplay by default is first person, but players have the option to play in third person mode. The core gameplay revolves around breaking and placing blocks. The game world is essentially composed of rough 3D objects‚Äîmainly cubes‚Äîthat are arranged in a fixed grid pattern and represent different materials, such as dirt, stone, various ores, water, and tree trunks. While players can move freely across the world, objects and items can only be placed at fixed locations relative to the grid. Players can gather these material blocks and place them elsewhere, thus allowing for various constructions.

Roblox is an online platform and game creation system where users can play games, socialize, and create their own games. It provides a user-friendly environment for developers to design games using the Roblox Studio, a powerful game development tool that employs the Lua programming language for scripting. Games on Roblox are hosted on the platform and can range across various genres, including adventure, role-playing, simulations, racing, and more.

Roblox is available on a variety of platforms, making it accessible to a wide audience. It can be played on Windows and macOS through the dedicated desktop apps, as well as on iPhones and iPads via the Roblox app in the App Store. Android users can access it through the Google Play Store, and Xbox One users can enjoy the platform through a dedicated app available in the Microsoft Store. Additionally, the Roblox website allows for account management, game browsing, and launching games.

Roblox is an online platform and game creation system where users can play games, socialize, and create their own games. It provides a user-friendly environment for developers to design games using the Roblox Studio, a powerful game development tool that employs the Lua programming language for scripting. Games on Roblox are hosted on the platform and can range across various genres, including adventure, role-playing, simulations, racing, and more.

Roblox is available on a variety of platforms, making it accessible to a wide audience. It can be played on Windows and macOS through the dedicated desktop apps, as well as on iPhones and iPads via the Roblox app in the App Store. Android users can access it through the Google Play Store, and Xbox One users can enjoy the platform through a dedicated app available in the Microsoft Store. Additionally, the Roblox website allows for account management, game browsing, and launching games.

snippet.title: Minecraft Live (September 2025)
snippet.description: Minecraft Live is a special show that gives you the inside info on everything happening in the world of Minecraft! The broadcast will be on September 27 at 7PM CEST/10AM PDT/1PM EDT.  Tune into to the show to learn more about what the developers have cooking up for Minecraft.

snippet.title: I Survived 100 Days as THE OWL in MINECRAFT!
snippet.description:
‚ñ∫ Check out my Friends MAC & OLLIE's Newest Movie Here: https://youtu.be/hRZht9_OB08

‚ñ∫ SUBSCRIBE to the Channel! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYPYEhWUvvKFgmgkLACagXA?sub_confirmation=1

The Owl is one of the most epic creatures to come from Roblox, which is why I decided to add him into Minecraft! Now for the next 99 nights and 100 days, I‚Äôll be surviving as the Owl, using my incredible abilities to stalk my victims and eliminate the cultist threats, while growing into bigger and stronger forms. Will I be able to defeat the King Frog, or will he take control of the forest? 

Additional Builds by https://www.youtube.com/@stan616/videos 

MODS USED:
Architectury API: https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/architectury-api
